snippet.title: Aretha (The Super Famicom) Game Sample - SNES/SFC
snippet.description:
Original Air Date: September 17th, 2008

This is a sample video for the first Aretha/アレサ game for the Super Famicom. A little bit of the video was truncated to get it to fit, though you probably won't notice it until the end (which skips walking back through the forest to go to the birth of Fang and a glimpse of Ariel as an adult). The game had the odd feature to battle enemy ranks and the music will "merge" with other tunes and end itself at different points as necessary, which attempts to highlight the music of the game.

You can read an in-depth article on the game at:

http://www.gamingsanctuary.com/Aretha_MR.html
